00:37:48,583 --> 00:37:51,768
And... it made me feel funny, so...

567
00:37:52,359 --> 00:37:53,145
Here.

568
00:37:57,258 --> 00:37:58,508
That's too bad.

569
00:37:58,826 --> 00:38:02,026
I was kind of getting
into the whole hot-for-teacher thing.

570
00:38:03,334 --> 00:38:04,615
You sure you're okay?

571
00:38:05,836 --> 00:38:07,284
Yeah.
False alarm.

572
00:38:10,501 --> 00:38:11,670
What about us?

573
00:38:12,780 --> 00:38:13,665
We're good...

574
00:38:14,288 --> 00:38:16,960
just like this. You press my buttons,
