575
00:38:17,128 --> 00:38:18,178
You mean...

576
00:38:32,815 --> 00:38:34,615
You do make me feel funny.

577
00:38:42,800 --> 00:38:43,987
You're not gonna die.

578
00:38:45,011 --> 00:38:46,396
I've accepted it.

579
00:38:46,521 --> 00:38:47,521
It's okay.

580
00:38:48,906 --> 00:38:51,468
In addition to high arches

